dcterms:creator: S. Mehrkanoon
dcterms:description: The Netherlands dataset contains hourly measurements of 6 weather variables including wind speed, wind direction, temperature, dew point, air pressure, and rain amount. Observations are collected from multiple weather stations including Schiphol, De Bilt, Leeuwarden, Eelde, Rotterdam, Eindhoven, and Maastricht. The dataset spans from January 1, 2011 to March 29, 2020, with training data from before January 2019 and testing data from January 2019 to March 2020.
dcterms:title: Netherlands Dataset

dcterms:creator: S. Mehrkanoon
dcterms:description: The Denmark dataset contains hourly observations of 4 weather variables including temperature, pressure, wind speed, and wind direction, collected from five weather stations: Aalborg, Aarhus, Esbjerg, Odense, and Roskilde. The dataset covers measurements from 2000 to 2010, with training data from before 2010 and testing data from 2010.
dcterms:title: Denmark Dataset
